{"tid":1126190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［駁唔到］台灣媽媽fb page 一圖總結香港既一國兩制","createTime":"2019-04-26T08:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T15:17:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7312bf94a3d50b4895d036de5b2f309cdb102800","tid":1126190,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XuuRFtX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuuRFtX.png&h=bfb939b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣媽媽護民主<br />\n<br />\n【台灣媽媽之香港議題】<br />\n＃一國兩制在香港<br />\n<br />\n香港自 1997 年回歸，在中國主張一國兩制的治理下，迄今也已超過 20 年了。<br />\n<br />\n北京政府為了沖淡港人的自我認同，很刻意地在引進內地的新移民，香港本來地就不大，在湧進了大量內地新移民後，不論是在居住環境、醫療品質、小孩的扶養與教育等各方面，品質都大打折扣。<br />\n<br />\n身為媽媽，看著在旁追逐嬉鬧的孩子們，忍心讓他們的未來變得如此慘澹不堪嗎？當然不行！<br />\n<br />\n明年一定要把握手上寶貴的一票，選出勇於向中共說不、拒絕一國兩制、捍衛台灣民主價值的總統！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n🏠香港的居住問題：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7qtAN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7qtAN&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=919ad4f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7qtAN</a><br />\n🚑港人的醫療現況：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Drhfom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Drhfom&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=f1eeef82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Drhfom</a><br />\n👨&zwj;⚕️擬立法開放中國內地醫師來港執業免甄試：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PtM40z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PtM40z&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=b843da2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PtM40z</a><br />\n🍼嬰兒奶粉短缺困境：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VhzPts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VhzPts&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=ec06c933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VhzPts</a><br />\n📖學童跨區就讀，上學大不易：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IJENIM\" 